description:
We are live today for a chat with the legend Billy Cobham​ to support his forthcoming  wTnS podcast episode.

Billy has played with Miles Davis​ (and many other jazz giants) and made some landmark records as a band leader himself. He also was a member of the iconic The Mahavishnu Orchestra​, and has toured with Peter Gabriel​, Jack Bruce and Bob Weir​!

Broadcast is a conjunction with Inside Out wTnS and Osiris Media.
title: wTnS Live w/ Billy Cobham
